name: Visible Thoughts: 018
description:
018 of the Visible Thoughts series.

How strange it is that life moves on. Regardless of its attachment to you or I, its goals, its weaknesses, its entire being - it is always moving on from past to future. It stops for no one, not even itself, perhaps not even for Death. Like the wind and seas, it ebbs and flows wherever it needs to be, and nothing else. There's a lesson in there somewhere, but we're too busy living to find out.
